Package SimpleUI

Class UiTween

java.lang.Object
SimpleUI.UiTween
public class UiTween extends Object
A class that represents a tween animation for a UI component. A tween animation is an animation that interpolates between two values over a period of time. This class can be used to animate the size, position, and color of a UI component.
Author:
haotian
